// Pulse Voyagers faction lair — a sky/water platform outpost.
//
// Layout (768 wide × 768 tall):
//
//   +----------------------------------------+
//   |▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒ ceiling ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒|
//   |                                        |
//   |                ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒                |
//   |              [Captain Pulse]           |  ← captain dais
//   |          ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒            |
//   |                                        |
//   |    ▒▒▒▒                  ▒▒▒▒          |
//   |     stepping stones (one-way)          |
//   |          ▒▒▒▒                          |
//   |                          ▒▒▒▒          |
//   | ▒▒▒                                    |
//   |                                ▒▒▒     |
//   | [Ent door]            [PlayerStart]    |
