//   +----------------------------------------+
//
// Movement contract: hop the staggered one-way stepping stones up
// to the central dais where Captain Pulse waits. The vertical climb
// uses OneWayPlatforms exclusively so the player can fall back to
// the floor and try again without the puzzle locking them in.

